<HEADLINE>
FANS PAY TOP DOLLAR FOR EARLY SCREENING OF `STAR WARS' 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JASON LLOREN  
 c.1999 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
