``k'' commentary news file.)  
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BORIS PLAYS GOD AGAIN; WEST CAN ONLY WATCH _ AND PRAY &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
