</P>
<P>
   (775 words) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Moved as BC-NO-MORE-NETANYAHOOS-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; IN PRAISE OF DAY TRADERS: DEMONIZED ONLINE GEEKS AREN'T ALL
BAD &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (650 words) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Moved as BC-GEEKS-ONLINE-STOCKS-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BEIJING'S WRATH IS JUSTIFIED, BUT COUNTERPRODUCTIVE &LR;  &QL;
