<P>
   BKN-HAWKS _ ATLANTA _ The Hawks don't have much time to relax
after a super Sunday _ on which they clinched their first-round
series and got home-court advantage (back at the Dome) for the next
round. It's the Knicks, beginning Tuesday. (Denberg, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   w/ BKN-KNICKS _ Once considered a longshot for the playoffs, the
Knicks not only made it but are in the second against the Hawks.
The GM was fired, the coach nearly was...but here they are. (Bunn,
