   KOSOVO-KLA _ TIRANA, Albania _ In-depth interview with young
Albanian-American who came back here to join the rebel group,
Kosovo Liberation Army, and fight for Kosovo. He is from New York
City and is part of the KLA's Atlantic Brigade, which is composed
of about 80 Americans, three of whom are women. They have been here
a few weeks and are fully trained and expect to head to the front
in a week or so. (Roughton, Cox News Service) WITH PHOTO
</P>
