<P>
   YUGOSLAVIA (Washington) _ NATO prepares to shelter up to 1
million Kosovar refugees in Albania for the winter, in case the war
does not end soon and Slobodan Milosevic unleashes a flood of new
exiles. By Charles A. Radin. 1300 words.
