 &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; BANKRUPTCY _ &LR;  Congress is weighing bills that would make it more
difficult for debtors to wipe away their credit card debt and other
unsecured debt through bankruptcy. Under discussion is a
controversial ``means'' test that would be applied to determine who
must repay and who can declare bankruptcy. Two Charts showing
bankruptcy rates in Calif and U.S. By Arthur M. Louis
</P>
