Michelle Akers loosens up before practice with members of the
United States Women's National Soccer Team. Akers broke the first
ground for women's soccer in America. But now at 33, she is
struggling to find a measure of durability for the 1999 Women's
World Cup, which begins on June19. (Todd Buchanan/New York Times
Photo)
